{"tid":1745854,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如果民意被騎劫，都係連登仔做成","createTime":"2019-11-22T12:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T18:05:55.000Z","uid":58335,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef57079cccd6714b81a8b915a65a936de2fc25e","tid":1745854,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"奶共派就全員投奶共派<br />\n<br />\n連登仔就繼續打內戰、射落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未贏先內鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時輸左<br />\n正苦就大條道理話香港大多數唔支持五大訴求<br />\n係少數暴徒搞出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反贏咗<br />\n中聯辦就會搵啲獻世派問責<br />\n<br />\n傳統犯民老屎忽係仆街<br />\n但白鴿黨後生個批今次都算係咁架啦<br />\n索tg都索唔少<br />\n<br />\n犯民未至於殺左你全家下？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住<br />\n共匪未有能力個時都要同國民黨合作！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fc3ec8fe8f25e2979548fabed03c0036df82430c","tid":1745854,"uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"講多句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係要犯民贏<br />\n係要奶共派輸</span></span>"},{"pid":"740c99b12c0e6021dfa8965447a4a723f23a1114","tid":1745854,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a8a99e6975a74139aaaebaba60b854b83c9e1e","tid":1745854,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"740c99b12c0e6021dfa8965447a4a723f23a1114","tid":1745854,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"記住投票呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c5ccb2ebe1d7513e2201b0f9e6c5c6ca67948d","tid":1745854,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48a8a99e6975a74139aaaebaba60b854b83c9e1e","tid":1745854,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"740c99b12c0e6021dfa8965447a4a723f23a1114","tid":1745854,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"記住投票呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"ofc la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322a1b641d219c679a3533babee1ae8e95fc78b5","tid":1745854,"uid":251265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:32:24.000Z","msg":"企圖抹黑民主派，呼籲手足投白票一律視為共諜。"},{"pid":"afd6246e40a349815b88fb72861d34b38596e3c8","tid":1745854,"uid":281802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:32:52.000Z","msg":"有一種藍，叫黃中藍。<br />\n<br />\n呢一種人，立場雖係黃，但邏輯同思維模式同藍冇分別。而不論藍黃，佢哋都有一個condom對象，叫記者。<br />\n<br />\n選舉近了，風向撚吹得如季後烈風。由屌傳媒報天橋游繩、曝露地下逃生路線，到法庭名單，總之就係要屌，唔係佢想睇嘅嘢就屌。<br />\n<br />\n我諗傳媒全行共識，最撚討厭嘅係「有事記者，冇事借歪」。一時又屌人影樣，到要認人又屌人唔影樣。要做嘢又話記者篤灰，瀨嘢又要記者俾片做證據。不如好好諗清楚，你期望傳媒角色係乜。如果你要傳媒吓吓無縫配合，咁即係逼記者歸邊，你做呢樣嘢，共產黨一樣做緊。每個記者都同你經歷緊一樣嘅惡劣環境、一樣嘅危險，甚至更危險，去盡力記錄、傳播所見所聞，呢個係記者職責所在，唔好強人所難要求記者只能做順你意思嘅嘢。記者臨場判斷做定唔做，係佢專業判斷，佢可以做，亦可以唔做。既然佢選擇做，就無可非議，佢係履行職責。有人會拿《飢餓的蘇丹》來說教，老實講呢個研究個案就冇結論嘅，你搵冇結論嘅嘢出來想推論啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n游繩營救係大街大巷進行，我諗你唔會天真到諗住800人可以完成游繩撤離，Popo到場只係時間問題。據我所知，已經唔係一開波就即刻Live，有幾多時間真係唔應該卸責落記者度。走水渠，你睇過《逃學威龍》，警察都睇過《逃學威龍》，Terminator帶走全部人係拍戲先有，走渠口本身就有風險，狗亦會有部署。唔係天真到諗住Popo會冇CIB跟住目標人物？冇人Mon線？<br />\n<br />\n最戅尻嘅係，法庭檢控名單都要屌。首先，呢個係公開資料，報公開資料都唔得，好嘢。其次，呢班冷氣軍師有冇了解過，242人分6個court，本身好多家屬同律師都唔知道自己親屬去咗邊處理，甚至好多人係未有律師、未通知屋企人接應，呢張名單真係要保密？晏晝先有人係IG瘋傳各間警署未有律師/家屬嘅名單，又唔屌IG D人？調轉用藍絲口吻，好唔見得光咩？當然咁樣公開身份會有不便，但唔報嘅時候你咪一樣會屌，「唔講名，到時被自殺都唔知咩事」，幾時開口鬧「黑記」？<br />\n<br />\n同前線勇武乜都唔割，一啲都唔難。同呢啲熱熱哋嘅黃中藍唔割先係考驗。<br />\n<br />\n#唔撚好condom記者唔該 #佢哋食顏色水食滾食彈唔少得過勇武 #呢班人每到選舉就會現身 #分化撚 #風向撚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/505125943/posts/10157573594160944?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F505125943%2Fposts%2F10157573594160944%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=296db052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/505125943/posts/10157573594160944?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"17555be16037ebacd2ef1a0a9b1ff2534a0b1d1c","tid":1745854,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a56df4d3162acd6f2756dc5161af6e9c3b8d34","tid":1745854,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"當係變相公投<br />\n唔係投人<br />\n係投理念:是否支持五大訴求<br />\n如果係既,泛民我都照投"},{"pid":"c937636aee3660f20aba9b3c8faef0b7ccaf5b7e","tid":1745854,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94a56df4d3162acd6f2756dc5161af6e9c3b8d34","tid":1745854,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"當係變相公投